text.__SUMMARY__: Macrozamia machinii is a species of cycad in the family Zamiaceae endemic to Queensland, Australia. It is found near Inglewood in the Darling Downs area.
text.References: Whitelock, Loran M. 2002. The Cycads. Portland: Timber Press. ISBN 0-88192-522-5
